detaileddescription.para: Implement the EMSK board GPIO object using the DesignWare GPIO device driver. Only need to implement some DesignWare GPIO structures and combine with EMSK GPIO hardware resources, like in C++ class instantiation. For example, in C++, define a class called gpio class gpio {
}; then instantiate the gpio class: gpio emsk_gpio_a;
